String.s: Alt-click parts of the HUD to announce their status ("I\'m wounded!", "I have 2 twigs.", "We need more drying racks."). ALT+SHIFT click to announce items.

Comment.s: --A version number so you can ask people if they are running an old version of your mod.
--This lets other players know if your mod is out of date. This typically needs to be updated every time there's a new game update.
--This lets clients know if they need to get the mod from the Steam Workshop to join the game

String.s: Detect the language based on language mods installed.
When announcing stats, show the numbers for your current and max stat.
When announcing a crafting recipe, whether to announce that you need a science machine or another prototyper.
When announcing stats, show an emoji for the stat (if using "Show current/max").
Whether to announce the durability/freshness of an item when announcing that you have it.
When controller inventory is open, allow the B/cancel button\nto be used to announce temperature\n(if you are using Combined Status).
When controller inventory is open, allow the SELECT/map button\nto be used to announce the season\n(if you are using Combined Status).
